name: Makeform
description: Makeform is an AI-powered form builder that enables users to create customizable forms using natural language. It is designed to simplify data collection for startups, creators, and teams. $FORM is a Solana-based community token launched to support the Makeform ecosystem. It functions as a digital collectible and may unlock access to features, perks, or digital merchandise in the future. $FORM does not represent ownership, equity, or financial rights.
